I'd want to contribute to society.

01:02:08.290 --> 01:02:09.859
You do.

01:02:09.891 --> 01:02:10.960
Hmm.

01:02:10.993 --> 01:02:17.498
Yes, we don't need pity.

01:02:17.531 --> 01:02:22.537
- We can contribute to society...
- Mm-hmm.

01:02:22.571 --> 01:02:26.909
- ...like anyone else.
- I agree.

01:02:26.942 --> 01:02:30.378
It's all about respect and trust

01:02:30.411 --> 01:02:33.281
and how big
and open your heart is

01:02:33.315 --> 01:02:38.454
even if you don't have
anything to begin with, hmm.

01:02:44.592 --> 01:02:47.328
We are really very happy
that you are here.

01:02:47.362 --> 01:02:48.764
Oh, thank you.

01:02:48.797 --> 01:02:53.402
Niladri's mother believes that his
love of music extended his life.

01:02:53.435 --> 01:02:56.304
Oh, at least my neonatal studies
proved useful.

01:02:56.337 --> 01:03:00.542
It would be best for all of us
if you made progress.

01:03:00.574 --> 01:03:04.545
There is an expert in Indian
classical raga and philosophy.

01:03:04.578 --> 01:03:06.347
You may like to meet her.

01:03:06.380 --> 01:03:08.283
- Yeah, I would love that.
- Yes.

01:03:45.520 --> 01:03:49.058
Let us all be happy.

01:03:50.192 --> 01:03:54.931
Let us all be free from illness.

01:03:55.563 --> 01:04:00.002
Let all see the auspicious.

01:04:01.536 --> 01:04:07.944
Let us all be free from misery.

