You know, most of the people
who lead a materialistic life

01:04:17.351 --> 01:04:21.022
often feel
they are missing something

01:04:22.223 --> 01:04:25.060
and they look for a purpose
in life.

01:04:28.130 --> 01:04:30.398
All problems in life

01:04:31.366 --> 01:04:37.639
arise from materialistic
longings and desires.

01:04:37.672 --> 01:04:39.976
They are mostly psychological,

01:04:41.109 --> 01:04:46.114
but all solutions are spiritual.

01:04:46.147 --> 01:04:50.285
Um, I need to learn
how music does things like that.

01:04:51.152 --> 01:04:52.721
You know what they say,

01:04:53.388 --> 01:04:59.328
admitting and realizing that you
have a problem is the first step.

01:04:59.795 --> 01:05:02.331
Dr. Sen sent me.

01:05:02.364 --> 01:05:03.432
Okay.

01:05:05.534 --> 01:05:08.503
Shanti. come with me.

01:05:10.172 --> 01:05:11.273
Thank you.

