01:08:13.455 --> 01:08:15.357
That's where I am.

01:08:15.389 --> 01:08:17.993
<i>Yes, but why are you shopping
in the men's department?</i>

01:08:18.026 --> 01:08:20.395
Max, it's late. Okay?

