The first one is
gonna be country.

01:09:23.624 --> 01:09:25.761
What you think?

01:09:47.749 --> 01:09:49.384
Next, rock and roll.

01:09:55.956 --> 01:09:57.759
Good, Yes.

01:09:59.427 --> 01:10:01.063
Oh, God.

