01:21:33.154 --> 01:21:35.089
- Help Sofia?
- Hmm.

01:21:35.121 --> 01:21:38.092
Jeeja and you
cannot get into the slum.

01:21:38.124 --> 01:21:39.793
It is too dangerous.

01:21:39.826 --> 01:21:42.696
You have to help me.

